{"tid":114844,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲去過美國東部旅行？","createTime":"2017-02-10T06:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T15:00:20.000Z","uid":24346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56e128cd691e9dac7624661fe0c12dc9b9ecacaa","tid":114844,"uid":24346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:08:23.000Z","msg":"暫定想六月去美國東部兩星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以下係想去嘅地方<br />\nnew york <br />\nwashington dc<br />\nniagara falls<br />\nboston <br />\n<br />\n去程hk飛ny<br />\n回程boston飛hk<br />\n<br />\n洗費貴唔貴？<br />\n我預機票食宿全包$20000-25000<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩景點/地方推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f17c5bcf6c3fd9867b68b9b8c6366d9bdc67c4","tid":114844,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:10:18.000Z","msg":"niagara falls無乜特別，特別係美國果邊"},{"pid":"64c4111a3d800c7e08238466cd3cf26386be6bfa","tid":114844,"uid":10643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:44:54.000Z","msg":"前年easter自己一個去左NYC玩14日<br />\n冇睇到niagara falls(因為知道係加拿大睇會好D)<br />\n我覺得NYC洗費唔算好貴<br />\n因為其實d野同香港比個度好抵屌<br />\n買到一袋二袋都唔算洗左好多錢<br />\n食個方面 想平就可以食多D food truck<br />\n豪D可以入餐廳食 不過最好搵人同你一齊share<br />\n美國佬D野食既份量真係多到食到你嘔<br />\n我覺得最貴係住宿 巴打你有睇岩個價又OK早D book會好D<br />\n我個陣貪平去左Queen個邊台灣人搞既民宿度住<br />\n後悔到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總結返個陣成個trip機票食宿洗費total用左大約洗左3萬蚊<br />\n<br />\n其他地方都未去過<br />\n<br />\n利申: 崇美撚<br />\n講起美國又好想再去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cc3973f8dabdd9cf938b7871f3160b7c3dc888","tid":114844,"uid":70343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:47:33.000Z","msg":"$20000你機票洗左幾多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNy住都至少都usd 40 above<br />\nDc boston相對平少少 我嗰陣住HI hostel都幾好<br />\n如果鐘意博物館dc都多野睇既<br />\nBoston真係好悶不過 3日都覺得多<br />\nNyc就好多野睇 至少留一個禮拜 <br />\n推薦Central park, top of the rock, chelsea market<br />\n無乜錢上島睇自由女神的話搭south ferry都夠皮架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nNyc好多野食 我嗰陣食太多asian food 推薦的話就淨係得shake shack喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw Niagara falls toronto睇靚啲同埋近好多"},{"pid":"8275174c6813f4ab2bb9189c93dce565659fb924","tid":114844,"uid":27280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T07:53:01.000Z","msg":"五六月可能去一趟NYC 有無巴絲有好介紹<br />\n例如有咩特別嘢可以join 或者地方推介<br />\n太Common嗰啲可免<br />\n仲有咩要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7c9fde8b4a799b69166000b850b72e3abd0c38","tid":114844,"uid":24346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>$20000你機票洗左幾多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機票我open jaw $5000<br />\n簽證都$1200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該搵3-4個朋友一齊去 住宿當$4000-5000<br />\n如果自駕會唔會方便啲？但驚泊車好煩"},{"pid":"0271e205c98979ca78f01a06ce21adbe6b32674e","tid":114844,"uid":24346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前年easter自己一個去左NYC玩14日<br />\n冇睇到niagara falls(因為知道係加拿大睇會好D)<br />\n我覺得NYC洗費唔算好貴<br />\n因為其實d野同香港比個度好抵屌<br />\n買到一袋二袋都唔算洗左好多錢<br />\n食個方面 想平就可以食多D food truck<br />\n豪D可以入餐廳食 不過最好搵人同你一齊share<br />\n美國佬D野食既份量真係多到食到你嘔<br />\n我覺得最貴係住宿 巴打你有睇岩個價又OK早D book會好D<br />\n我個陣貪平去左Queen個邊台灣人搞既民宿度住<br />\n後悔到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總結返個陣成個trip機票食宿洗費total用左大約洗左3萬蚊<br />\n<br />\n其他地方都未去過<br />\n<br />\n利申: 崇美撚<br />\n講起美國又好想再去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解後悔都喊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該同朋友住airbnb"},{"pid":"c6c55365cb9ddda5896f7d4190e9431a1f2059af","tid":114844,"uid":53388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:50:32.000Z","msg":"已買機票6月尾去NYC留名<br />\n想去nyc同toronto坐通宵greyhound 10幾個鐘會唔會好on居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋住宿應該搵酒店定airbnb好 我見一晚都差唔多要$1000左右"},{"pid":"8103831de406e56d4e320e67d324ce3bf5c527bf","tid":114844,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T14:59:08.000Z","msg":"記得去食halal guys<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb23a94d8a73c0df389cda292a8cc01083c1140","tid":114844,"uid":31618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得去食halal guys<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重有黃昏睇Brooklyn bridge <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9616b687c561f7550b705615b86e6c21ea6282b6","tid":114844,"uid":70343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已買機票6月尾去NYC留名<br />\n想去nyc同toronto坐通宵greyhound 10幾個鐘會唔會好on居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋住宿應該搵酒店定airbnb好 我見一晚都差唔多要$1000左右</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOk la 我試過係boston搭overnight bus去toronto 訓下教就到啦但記得轉車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nNyc check下hostelworld可能唔使咁貴"},{"pid":"455d15d8e669694bd211ae304c4c1d8f3801ded8","tid":114844,"uid":70343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>$20000你機票洗左幾多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機票我open jaw $5000<br />\n簽證都$1200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該搵3-4個朋友一齊去 住宿當$4000-5000<br />\n如果自駕會唔會方便啲？但驚泊車好煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCity to city有greyhound好方便<br />\nCity入面全部都有metro 巴士<br />\n最多咪去niagara嗰程自駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw係nyc or boston應該去睇nba<br />\n唔係籃球撚既我表示都真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2x usd坐下山頂位都抵啊"},{"pid":"a2e94bd5d58575b9ae32c59387d69ea47eee9ade","tid":114844,"uid":24346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T13:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>$20000你機票洗左幾多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機票我open jaw $5000<br />\n簽證都$1200<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該搵3-4個朋友一齊去 住宿當$4000-5000<br />\n如果自駕會唔會方便啲？但驚泊車好煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCity to city有greyhound好方便<br />\nCity入面全部都有metro 巴士<br />\n最多咪去niagara嗰程自駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw係nyc or boston應該去睇nba<br />\n唔係籃球撚既我表示都真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2x usd坐下山頂位都抵啊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nnba有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果city 地鐵方便就唔自駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n泊車好似仲麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2137d05e3eb6ff74bf30ffe39bc1e5e5f20015","tid":114844,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:46:46.000Z","msg":"new york 去 dc 。坐唐人街旅遊巴平d又密d. <br />\n<br />\n坐過toronto overnight bus 去boston. greyhound 都ok. 但中間要轉車。<br />\nnew york 返toronto坐過火車，舒服過巴士好多。<br />\n你可以比較下內陸機有無平<br />\n記憶中greyhound唔平<br />\n<br />\n(利申 1x年去過以上行程only"},{"pid":"370522b35129b01e66cb0d37827cb05cfac1f55e","tid":114844,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"係ny,boston,dc都唔洗自駕。全部都有metro/bus好方便<br />\nny自駕=係香港/東京自駕。玩自己咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0224116963639e3864ecd42962784713a289543","tid":114844,"uid":83938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:58:45.000Z","msg":"前年去過Boston (3 days) -&gt; NY (9 days) -&gt; Philadelphia (2 days)-&gt; Washington (4 days)<br />\n全部搭greyhound 但早買飛 價錢記得都OK<br />\n全部住HI Hostel 幾高質"},{"pid":"97af06509666e84ac0c50b5c505196cc5eb6053c","tid":114844,"uid":83938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T15:00:20.000Z","msg":"同埋主要係徒步去景點 NY就經常搭metro<br />\n利申: 冇牌jj"}]}